2009-12-27  Peter Schuster   <typo3@peschuster.de>

	* makes use of typo3 autoloader
	* raised version requirements for typo3 to v4.3.0
	* on ajax request $GLOBALS['TSFE']->id is set (e.g. for tx_smilie)
	* adjusted smilie hook to tx_smilie version 1.0.0
	* changed type of ajax request for shoutbox update to 'get'
	* removed 'no messages available' string from ajax response
	* feature: added blacklist (comma separated list)
	* feature: added auto archive function (typoscript: maxAge)

